#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.trunc.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.trunc"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc:1 of
msgid "Return the truncated value of the input, element-wise."
msgstr "按元素方式返回输入的截断值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc:3 of
msgid ""
"The truncated value of the scalar `x` is the nearest integer `i` which is"
" closer to zero than `x` is. In short, the fractional part of the signed "
"number `x` is discarded."
msgstr ""
"标量 `x` 的截断值是距离零更近的最近整数 `i`。简而言之，有符号数 `x` 的"
"小数部分被丢弃。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc:7 of
msgid "Input data."
msgstr "输入数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc:9 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须与输入广播一致。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc:14 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc:19 of
msgid "**y** -- The truncated value of each element in `x`."
msgstr "**y** -- `x` 中每个元素的截断值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ceil`, :py:obj:`floor`, :py:obj:`rint`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.trunc.trunc:25 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

